<center><a href=""><span class="title">Wp Plugin Wp Display Users</span></a></center>

<h3><u>Plugin Details</u></h3><div>Plugin Name: <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-display-users/" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" target="_blank">wp-plugin : wp-display-users</a></div>
<div>Effected Version : 2.0.0 (and most probably lower version's if any)</div>
<div>Vulnerability : <a href="/category/injection/">Injection</a></div>
<div>Minimum Level of Access Required : Administrator</div>
<div>CVE Number : CVE-2021-24400</div>
<div>Identified by : <a href="/author/syed_sheeraz_ali/">Syed Sheeraz Ali</a></div>
<div><a href="https://wpscan.com/plugin/wp-display-users/" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow" target="_blank">WPScan Reference URL</a></div>
 
<h3><u>Disclosure Timeline</u></h3>
<ul>
	<li>

<div>May 9, 2021: Issue Identified and Disclosed to WPScan</div>

	</li>
	
	<li>
	May 13, 2021 : Plugin  Closed</li>
	
	
	<li>June 10, 2021 : CVE Assigned</li>
	
	<li>August 22, 2021 : Public Disclosure</li>
</ul>



<h3><u>Technical Details</u></h3>

<p>Vulnerable File: <code>/includes/forms/display-users-manage-role.php#180</code></p>
<p>Vulnerable Code block and parameter:</p>
<p>Administrator level SQLi for parameter <code>id</code> <a href="https://plugins.trac.wordpress.org/browser/wp-display-users/trunk/includes/forms/display-users-manage-role.php#180" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">/includes/forms/display-users-manage-role.php#180</a>
</p>
<pre><code>180:	$display_users_data = $wpdb-&gt;get_row( 'SELECT * FROM '.$wpdb-&gt;prefix.'display_users WHERE id='.$_GET['id'].'' );
</code></pre><h2 id="poc-screenshots">PoC Screenshots</h2>
